This paper is about a comparative study of open source deep learning frameworks, which involves machine learning algorithms, image processing, and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
